[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/help_suit_game_try"]
[Student "S"]
{You have an invitational strength hand, but there are TWO suits you could use some help in. In this case you pick the suit where the Help would be most welcome. If partner can Help in \Ds that will probably be all you need to make game.

So you bid 3\D and partner puts you right to 4\S.}

